# Code owners for Gommage.
#
# Syntax: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-customizations/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Gommage is currently maintained by a single person. This file exists so that
# GitHub auto-requests a review on PRs touching security-critical paths, and so
# that branch-protection rules with "require review from code owners" cannot be
# bypassed for those paths.
#
# Ordering matters: later, more-specific rules override earlier ones.

# --- Default owner for everything not matched below ------------------------
*                                 @Arakiss

# --- Security-critical cores -----------------------------------------------
# Any edit here is a decision-surface change. Keep the review explicit.
